videos.headline: Oregon long TD pass adds to lead
videos.description: QB Justin Herbert connects with a wide open Brenden Schooler for the 37-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ducks rushing TD boosts lead to 17
videos.description: QB Justin Herbert keeps it and sneaks in from 7-yards away to add to the Oregon lead.

videos.headline: Cal INT yields redzone opportunity
videos.description: QB Taylor Alie gets picked off by Jordan Kunaszyk who returns it 53-yards.

videos.headline: Cal capitalizes on INT with TD
videos.description: QB Ross Bowers finds Jordan Veasy who fights for the 18-yard touchdown to get Cal on the board.

videos.headline: Ducks punch in another rushing TD
videos.description: RB Kani Benoit forces his way in for the rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: Cal answers with long passing TD
videos.description: QB Ross Bowers passes it to Kanawai Noa who sprints down the sideline for the 75-yard score.

videos.headline: Oregon forces strip sack and recovers the ball
videos.description: Cal QB Ross Bowers is stripped behind the line and loses the football, recovered by the Ducks deep in Bears territory.

videos.headline: Ducks capitalize on turnover with rushing TD
videos.description: RB Tony Brooks-James keeps his legs moving and finds the endzone to put the Ducks up by 21.

videos.headline: Ducks capitalize on turnover with rushing TD
videos.description: RB Tony Brooks-James keeps his legs moving and finds the endzone to put the Ducks up by 21.

videos.headline: Cal hangs around with TD pass
videos.description: QB Ross Bowers passes to wide open Vic Wharton III for the easy score to cut the lead to 14.

videos.headline: Oregon adds 5th rushing TD
videos.description: RB Darrian Felix moves around the outside and runs in for the touchdown to cap off big rushing day for Oregon.
